					<font size="12" pdfFontName="net/sf/jasperreports/fonts/dejavu/DejaVuSerif-Italic.ttf" isPdfEmbedded="true"/>
				</textElement>
				<text><![CDATA[The questions are colour-coded. <font color="#ec6607">Orange</font> criteria are <font color="#ec6607">'shall'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is required. <font color="#004280">Blue</font> criteria are <font color="#004280">'should'</font> criteria, i.e. meeting them is recommended. Making true and accurate statements will help you get genuine feedback on your sample collection procedures and, as a result, improve certain processes in the future.]]></text>
			</staticText>
